snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc - Tokubetsu-Hen Campaign Girl '97 (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Private Idol Disc: Tokubetsu-Hen Campaign Girl '97 is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1997.
